|| … I started powershaping at @medlinksaesthetics in November of 2024 - These sessions need to be incorporated with a healthy regime. I have a balanced routine that includes: workouts 4-5 days a week, eating mindfully, consuming my supplements and living a sustainable lifestyle. I am so happy with the results. Let me know what you think? ☺️

I’m attaching the first reel in the comments, so you can see the difference from then to now!

If you have any other questions, drop it in the comments or contact Medlinks Aesthetics ✨
